[15/01/2019 15:46:06] <font color="#00ff00">"Saber y Ganar",</font>
[15/01/2019 15:46:16] <font color="#00ff00">un programa presentado</font>
[15/01/2019 15:46:16] <font color="#00ff00">por Jordi Hurtado.</font>
